Package: birdtrends
Title: Estimate Trends Based On Modelled Annual Indices Or Related Inputs
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person("Genevieve", "Perkins", , "genevieve.c.perkins@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2663-5904")),
             person("Adam C.", "Smith", role = "aut",
                      email = "adam.smith2@canada.ca"))
Description: This package provides a flexible framework to generate trends, based on actual or modeled annual indices data. This package was designed to undertake assessment of 2016 Partners In Flight Landbird Conservation objectives. 
